			x: -8.0d
			y: -1.5d
		}
		{
			dependencies: ["41C1000000000001"]
			description: ["The &eMelter&r does the opposite - powered heat turns cobblestone back into lava. Paired with the Solidifier, you have an infinite loop of stone and lava with no crucible babysitting."]
